font Go Mono:size=12
tabs 4
expandtabs false
autoindent true
snarfselection primary
followfocus true

# Here be bindings
bind C space command jump

## Goblinkeys Navigation
bind * Down command linedown
bind * Up command lineup
bind * Left command charleft
bind * Right command charright
bind C u command charright
bind C o command charleft
#bind C . command lineup
bind C e command linedown
bind C BackSpace command delword
bind C d command del
#bind C , command eol
bind C p command bol
bind C Home command bol

## CUA, with Goblin flair
bind C c command snarf
bind C g command cut
bind C r command paste
bind C s command write
bind C f command search
bind C z command send u

# Chords
chord 1 13 cut current
